<br>
Well hopefully I havent done too much of a disservice to our chosen profession.<br>
<br>
Comments and flames are welcome.  and I hope you take the time to post to the devcorner ... I think a letter writing campagn may help, we know for sure that a petition on this board will be ignored. <p>Ragtooth Irongrip <br>
